name: An artist inside the art
description:
This photograph was taken outside the Brahma temple,Pushkar. Brahma temple in Pushkar is a rare religious site that is dedicated to the lord of creation, Lord Brahma. And this temple in Pushkar is the only Brahma temple in the whole world.The Pushkar Brahma Temple dates from the 14th century.

This artist was sitting outside the temple drawing a portrait of Lord Brahma himself, I asked him if I could capture his beautiful art. He replied with a spark in his eyes, "Yeah Sure".
